title: Valerijonas
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Lithuanian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A primarily vegetarian restaurant that occasionally serves fish, is located in a health store/tea shop. Only 4 tables. Dishes of the day. 2nd floor for tea-drinking. Tea ceremonies and health consultations available.
